Also guys as a second thought....
Please remember TNA is filmed live now so maybe this was just one of those nights if you know what I mean. I still enjoyed the show and even though as said before the sound does drop out. It is only when the guys are cleaning the ring in between matches. The show itself is still all there. TY Scene4all for ALL your downloads.

Thank you scene4all. I'm a big fan of your downloads of wrestling. You are the best :) Keep download more :)

Please tell me that people aren't as stupid as they seem... it says "UNCUT". Therefore, it means the commercials are NOT in there, but the pause in between (where the commercials would be) IS in there! Therefore... uncut! Is that really that hard to figure out? :-/ Seriously?
